name: Create Google Calendar events from new Microsoft 365 worksheet rows
description:
Every time you add a new row to a Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet, Make will automatically create a Google Calendar event.

Your Microsoft 365 Excel worksheet has to contain headers. The template uses [this worksheet](https://1drv.ms/x/s!AjJKBs6vWrtygRvWpqS9Usnd43sU?e=gg9c3p).
